<html>
<head>
    <title>Shrinivasan Neelamegam</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>

    <link href="/stylesheets/materialize.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/stylesheets/style.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.3.10/angular.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/angular-ui-router/0.2.10/angular-ui-router.js"></script>

    <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.1.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/angularApp.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/materialize.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery.fittext.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery.lettering.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery.textillate.js"></script>
    <style> .glyphicon-thumbs-up { cursor:pointer } </style>
</head>
<body ng-app="flapperNews">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s12 m12 l12">

          <ui-view></ui-view>
      </div>
        
    </div>
       <script type="text/ng-template" id="/posts.html">
          
            <div ng-repeat="post in posts | orderBy:'-upvotes'">
                  <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up"
                        ng-click="incrementPostUpvotes(post)"></span>
                  {{post.upvotes}}
                  <span style="font-size:20px; margin-left:10px;">
                    <a ng-show="post.link" href="{{post.link}}">
                        {{post.title}}
                    </a>
                    <span ng-hide="post.link">
                      {{post.title}}
                    </span>
                  </span>
                  <span>
                      <a href="#/posts/{{post._id}}">Comments</a>
                  </span>
        </div>
      </script>

    <script type="text/ng-template" id="/home.html">

      <div class="demo card-panel">
        <div class="chip">
          <img src="/stylesheets/neel.jpg" alt="Contact Person">
            Shrinivasan Neelamegam
        </div>
        <p class="flow-text">I am a web developer with deep knowledge of HTML, CSS, Javascript. I have extensive hands on experience with Object Oriented Javascript, Responsive web design, Javascript libraries and frameworks like AngularJS. I’m proficient in creating features, functional components, reusable widgets for a wide variety of business applications using web technologies. In addition to creating reusable components, I also focus on making performance enhancements, track metrics using google analytics, make the products compatible with mobile, tablet devices. I have worked with different content management platforms including Drupal. I’m currently working on developing single page applications using AngularJS, JSON, Node.js. Feel free to contact me by sending a message below</p>
      </div>

        <form ng-submit="addPost()">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="form-group col s12 m10">
                <input type="text"
                       class="form-control"
                       placeholder="Message"
                       ng-model="title"></input>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col s12 m2">
            <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action" onclick="Materialize.toast('Message sent!', 2000)">Submit
              <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
            </button>
            </div>
          </div>  
        </form>


           
    </script>
    <script>
    $(function () {
             $('.demo')
              .textillate({ in: { effect: 'flipInY' }});
           });
    </script>
</body>
</html>